commit.message:
Add advice on sample rate.

It's good to have the sample rate be an integer multiple or divisor of
the source material's sample rate, or even better, have it be the
same.
Add alt texts to the images

Delete traling whitespace

Let's do this first, in a separate commit.
jack: added -c command line argument to disable automatically connecting jack ports to physical outputs
jack: unregister jack ports before creating new ports, otherwise ports can't be created after a configuration change
